Creation of validated raw_data class

new_raw_data.Rd

The wrapper function for the constructor of the raw_data and its validator. Used in raw_data function.

Usage

new_raw_data(
  metabolomics_matrix,
  LOD_table,
  NA_info,
  metabolites,
  samples,
  group,
  removed,
  completed,
  cv
)

Value

raw_data object.
